    <h1>DPT_ProjectileSurfaceImpact</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">
        Modular Surface Reaction &amp; VFX Cleanup Utility<br>
        <span class="subtitle-desc">Provides robust, contextual material variations by analyzing the exact physics layers involved in the collision. This enables ammunition types to dynamically map dirt, stone, wood, or water elements to distinct visual effects, audio arrays, and physical vertex-mesh surface marks (cracks, molehills, or trenches).</span>
    </div>

    <nav class="quick-nav" aria-label="Quick Navigation">
